He's afraid. You can hear the tone.

0:01:33.140,0:01:36.200
He said, " Yes".

0:01:36.220,0:01:38.700
He's not a witch.

0:01:38.760,0:01:40.760
Your brother said that you are a witch.

0:01:40.760,0:01:41.260
Yes.

0:01:41.260,0:01:42.560
Are you a witch?

0:01:42.560,0:01:43.320
Yes.

0:01:43.320,0:01:45.140
Do you want to hear from me?

0:01:45.140,0:01:45.900
Yes, man of God.

0:01:45.900,0:01:49.200
I will pray for you people. These two are not witches.

0:01:49.240,0:01:51.720
I am the only person in our family that remains.

0:01:51.720,0:01:53.160
All my seniors have died.

0:01:53.160,0:01:56.400
I am the only person that can take care of them. They have rejected them.

0:01:56.400,0:01:59.300
Ok. Only you remain in the family?

0:01:59.300,0:01:59.800
Yes.

0:01:59.800,0:02:01.160
Everybody else has died?

0:02:01.160,0:02:01.840
Yes.

0:02:01.840,0:02:03.380
And you are the only person that is taking care of them?

0:02:03.380,0:02:04.640
Yes. We're three at home.

0:02:04.640,0:02:06.900
Ok, then I will join your family.

0:02:06.900,0:02:08.900
Thank you, man of God.

0:02:08.980,0:02:12.200
Thank you Jesus!

0:02:12.280,0:02:14.040
Tell me, how do you want me to join?

0:02:14.040,0:02:17.680
Do you want to take me as your senior brother or your junior brother

0:02:17.680,0:02:19.980
