0:02:19.980,0:02:25.000
As my father.

0:02:25.040,0:02:28.020
Ok. Jesus will be our father.

0:02:28.040,0:02:32.200
So, we will just be members of the family.

0:02:32.260,0:02:38.700
I want to see you and see what we can do to move the family forward.

0:02:38.780,0:02:39.900
Thank you, Jesus!

