What are you doing for a living?

0:02:41.980,0:02:44.500
Somebody borrowed me money to sell recharge cards -

0:02:44.500,0:02:45.720
since my mother has gone.

0:02:45.720,0:02:48.680
Ok, someone borrowed you money to sell recharge cards.

0:02:48.680,0:02:49.340
Yes.

0:02:49.360,0:02:50.680
And that is what you are doing?

0:02:50.680,0:02:52.140
Have you returned the money?

0:02:52.140,0:02:52.640
No.

0:02:52.640,0:02:53.640
You have not returned the money?

0:02:53.640,0:02:54.320
Yes.

0:02:54.320,0:02:56.160
How much did the person borrow you?

0:02:56.160,0:02:59.800
He borrowed me 30,000 naira.

0:02:59.820,0:03:01.940
I borrowed some money and joined the money together and took

0:03:01.940,0:03:03.400
them from Akwa Ibom to this place.

0:03:03.480,0:03:04.860
From which state are you?

0:03:04.860,0:03:06.600
Akwa Ibom.

0:03:06.680,0:03:08.080
They are not witches.

0:03:08.080,0:03:13.860
It is the situation in the house that makes everybody a witch or a wizard.

0:03:13.860,0:03:20.460
And their situation is so grave that, if they grow big in the nearest future

0:03:20.460,0:03:24.300
and you people are not delivered today, they will call you a wizard.

0:03:24.300,0:03:26.880
Assume that you are in their position and they are in your position.

0:03:26.880,0:03:29.400
They too will call you wizard.

0:03:29.480,0:03:32.400
They are looking for where the problem is coming from

0:03:32.400,0:03:34.900
and anybody can be a scapegoat.

0:03:45.940,0:03:52.300
Who is a witch now?

0:03:52.360,0:03:55.500
Who is a wizard?

0:03:55.580,0:03:59.600
You are free. You are all children of God.

0:03:59.620,0:04:01.900
Live at peace. Thank you.

0:04:01.960,0:04:04.860
L'homme de Dieu vient de declarer que l'enfant n'est pas un sorcier -

0:04:04.860,0:04:07.200
contrairement a ce que la famille disait.

0:04:07.260,0:04:14.300
Thank you, Jesus!

