Last Friday, I came here to attend the prayer line

0:05:10.660,0:05:12.700
because of these two children.

0:05:12.700,0:05:13.980
They accused them.

0:05:13.980,0:05:16.300
They said that they are the ones that killed my mom.

0:05:16.320,0:05:19.700
I then took them to the Synagogue Church Of All Nations.

0:05:19.700,0:05:25.600
When we were here at the prayer line, the man of God touched my brothers.

0:05:25.680,0:05:30.300
I then shouted, "Please help me, man of God, help my brothers".

0:05:30.340,0:05:33.200
They accused them, saying that they are witches.

0:05:33.200,0:05:36.900
The man of God told me that these children are not witches.

0:05:36.900,0:05:40.820
They said that these children are the ones that killed my mom.

0:05:40.820,0:05:42.380
My mother's corpse is on the ground.

