They never buried my mother's corpse.

0:05:44.100,0:05:45.660
They didn't take her to the mortuary.

0:05:45.660,0:05:48.400
They embalmed my mother and kept her body in the house.

0:05:48.420,0:05:52.100
So, these children, my father sent them away.

0:05:52.120,0:05:57.200
They rejected us and we have nowhere to go - nowhere to live.

0:05:57.220,0:06:02.700
I struggled to get money to try and do my mother's burial.

0:06:02.720,0:06:03.900
There was no money.

0:06:03.980,0:06:06.140
So, my friends started to call me.

0:06:06.140,0:06:10.040
They said that since my mother sent those ones out of the house,

0:06:10.040,0:06:13.800
they used to sleep under the transformer, in the rain.

0:06:13.860,0:06:15.360
You can look at their body now.

0:06:15.360,0:06:20.400
When you see their body, you would see that these people used to sleep under the transformer.

0:06:20.440,0:06:24.040
